FastCraft mod will not be loaded due to Thermos compatibility issues. If you still wish to enable it, add "-thermos.fastcraft.disable=false

意思是：你把fastcraft这个只能装在客户端的mod装在了服务端
            如果你坚持想为服务端装载Fastcraft，请在你的开服脚本内加一段-thermos.fastcraft.disable=false
